  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this prospective multicenter cohort study is to examine long-term medical
      outcomes, quality of life, and medical resource utilization in elderly patients (&gt;= 65 years)
      with acute venous thromboembolism (i.e., acute pulmonary embolism and/or deep vein
      thrombosis)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
